Class TextIntWritable

java.lang.Object
  edu.ucla.sspace.hadoop.TextIntWritable
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<TextIntWritable>, Writable, WritableComparable<TextIntWritable>
public class TextIntWritable
extends Object
implements WritableComparable<TextIntWritable>

A special-purpose tuple Writable for storing text and int values together in one object. This class is designed to record the co-occurrence a term and a relative offset indicating the distance from the focus term.

This class follows the general contract for Writable by providing a static deserialization method and a no-arg constructor.
